Class AbstractController<T extends Comparable<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.szut.simNil.binaryMaple.gui.AbstractController<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of the tree
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DoubleController, IntegerController, StringController
    public abstract class AbstractController<T extends Comparable<T>>
extends Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    Controller for the GUI it is abstract for different data type like string, int and double and they need different data conversion from the input
